00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:04,280
♪Kau yang sudah goyah♪

516
00:32:06,280 --> 00:32:11,030
♪Kau terus mundur♪

517
00:32:14,380 --> 00:32:17,630
♪Menungguku datang menyelamatkanmu♪

518
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:20,600
♪Dengan segala kelembutan♪

